-- Gref Says Tax Hikes to Erase Sberbank Savings From Cutting 15% of Staff
-- B y   M a r i a   L e v i t o v
-- 2010-11-19T07:43:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-19/gref-says-tax-hikes-to-erase-sberbank-savings-from-cutting-15-of-staff.html
OAO Sberbank Chief Executive Officer
German Gref said tax increases next year will erase savings the
lender made in the last two and a half years by cutting about 15
percent of staff and “optimizing” other procedures. He spoke
at a conference in Moscow today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Levitov in Moscow at 
